{
  "id": "adv_event_2209_01_03",
  "title": "未来とつながるマジカルメロディ 3話 ありのままの想い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――歌詞制作が始まって、数日後……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Few days after the lyric production began……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うーん……あまりしっくりこうへんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… It doesn't quite feel right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "回りくどいって言うか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like going around in circles…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ストレート過ぎるとチープになりそうだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if it's too straightforward‚ it might feel cheap…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "逆に、こういう表現はどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about this expression?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "うまく間を取れてると思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it strikes a good balance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、でも待って。前後の脈絡が少し変になるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ but wait. The context before and after might get a little awkward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "…………う～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "このまま唸っとってもしゃあないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no point just grumbling like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "少し休憩でもしよか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should we take a short break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええ。……作詞って、想像以上に難しいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Writing lyrics is more difficult than I imagined.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、簡単とも思ってなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I didn't think it would be easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "語彙力、メロディーとの兼ね合い、コンセプト……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Vocabulary‚ balance with melody‚ concept…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "いろんなこと考えなあかんからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are many things to consider.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "伝えたいこととか言葉にしたいことって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many things I want to convey and express in words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "ホントは沢山あるんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can't put everything into lyrics‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "全部は詞に起こせないし、ただ、欠けてもダメだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and even if something is missing‚ it won't work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "うわーん、難しいよぅ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uwaaan‚ it's difficult!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（どうするのがいいんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(What should we do?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "（私達だけじゃ、実力が伴ってない？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Do we lack the skills to do this on our own?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（……いや、そんな弱気じゃダメ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…No‚ being so pessimistic won't help)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "（まだ、出来ることはあるはず）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(There must still be something we can do)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いっそのこと、誰かに相談してみる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about asking someone else?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういえば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yeah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん達サニピも、作詞経験あるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan and the Sunny Peace girls have experience in writing lyrics‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……そうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに三人だけで考えるのも限界だし……よしっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perhaps relying on just the three of us won't be enough… Alright.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お疲れ様……ってどうした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello… Oh‚ what's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どこか出掛けるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you going somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ……{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "実は、ちょうど相談しに行こうと思ってたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ we was just about to go and ask for help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "相談……作詞に関してか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Help… about lyrics?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "結構苦戦していたようだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seemed to be struggling quite a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あら、知っとったのに声も掛けず静観してたん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ so you knew and just silently watched?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "人が悪いなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're quite mean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "頼る前に助け船を出されるのも、悔しいだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be frustrating to be thrown a lifeline before asking for help‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
